# Lesson 05 Livebook: Historical Validation

Rewrite mode is no longer enough. The aggregate now asks whether the replayed past was actually possible.

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:wormhole_protocol, path: "../05_historical_validation"}
])
```

## Run The Historical Validation Scenario

```elixir
story = WormholeProtocol.historical_validation_story!()

%{
  impossible: story.impossible,
  available_oxygen: story.available_oxygen,
  allocations: story.allocations
}
```

## Confirm That The Accepted Present Stayed Intact

```elixir
Enum.map(story.allocations, & &1.command_id)
```
